tooltip.add_images_to_default_group: Ta atomatik ƙara wuraren aiki zuwa rukuni na ainihi lokacin da aka ƙara sabbin wuraren aiki.

tooltip.api_private_key: Maɓallin masu zaman kansu ana amfani da shi don nuna buƙata tsakanin abubuwan haɗin Kasm.
tooltip.api_public_cert: Maɓallin jama'a da aka yi amfani da shi don inganta kiran API na ciki.
tooltip.auto_agent: Sanya wakili ta atomatik lokacin da ya kira.
tooltip.debug_retention: Yawan sa'o'i don riƙe rajistan ayyukan Kasm na gida. Gargadi - duba Takardar Kasm kafin daidaitawa.
tooltip.default_cpu_allocation_method: Yana saita tsohuwar dabarar CPU don hotunan kwastu. Zaɓuɓɓukan inganci sune kwatancen ko hannun jari.
tooltip.default_vm_rdp_connection_settings: Saitunan haɗin kai na VM RDP.
tooltip.default_vm_ssh_connection_settings: Saitunan haɗin kai don VM SSH Temsions.
tooltip.default_vm_vnc_connection_settings: Saitunan haɗin kai don zaman VM VM VM.
tooltip.enable_kasm_auth: Buƙatar buƙatun abokin ciniki zuwa kasm don abun ciki kamar saukar da abubuwan saukarwa tare da alamar zaman mai amfani.
tooltip.forward_inter_zone_agent_requests: Lokacin da tuntuɓar wakilai a cikin wani yanki daban, buƙatun ci gaba ta hanyar adireshin wakili na yanki.
tooltip.guardian_interval: Yawan seconds tsakanin mai sarrafa API bincike na wakilin data kasance, da wadatar Kasm.
tooltip.guardian_provision_threads: Yawan zaren mai sarrafa API yana amfani da kayan gado da kayan tanadi.
tooltip.hec_token: Alamar HEC da aka yi amfani da ita don ingantacciyar rajistan ayyukan zuwa uwar garken SPUNK.
tooltip.host_dead_expiration: Yawan seconds tun lokacin da aka bincika na ƙarshe na wakili kafin a yiwa matattu. Ana lalata sabobin da suka mutu ta atomatik idan sun kasance mai tsauri.
tooltip.host_missing_expiration: Yawan seconds tun lokacin da aka bincika na ƙarshe na wakili kafin a yiwa matattu.
tooltip.http_method: Hanyar HTTP don amfani, kyawawan dabi'u suna da post kuma saka. SPOWKK yana amfani da post yayin amfani da API yana amfani da shi
tooltip.https_insecure: Saita zuwa ga gaskiya idan mai nisa mai nisa bashi da ingantaccen sa hannu ta hanyar takardar shaidar jama'a.
tooltip.kasm_auth_domain: Overrode yankin da aka yi amfani da shi a cikin kuki na zaman da Kasm.
tooltip.keepalive_expiration: Abokan ciniki a kai a kai suna tura buƙatun da ke cikin kullun lokacin da suka shiga cikin kasm. Wannan darajar ita ce yawan seconds wani Kasm zai ci gaba da kasancewa mai himma bayan an karɓi kiyayewa na ƙarshe.
tooltip.launcher_background_url: URL da aka yi amfani da shi don tantance asalin hoton don ƙaddamar.
tooltip.license_server_url: URL zuwa uwar garken Kasm Layin.
tooltip.log_host: Kalmar mai masauki ko adireshin IP na uwar garken shiga mai nisa, ba a zartar da shiga cikin shiga ciki ba.
tooltip.log_port: Tashar jiragen ruwa don amfani don shiga sadarwa.
tooltip.log_protocol: Yarjejeniyar shiga da aka yi amfani da ita, da aka ba da izinin ƙimar suna cikin ciki, https, splunk, da kuma nazarin
tooltip.log_retention: Yawan kwanaki don riƙe rajistan ayyukan Kasm na gida. Gargadi - duba Takardar Kasm kafin daidaitawa.
tooltip.login_assistance: Yana ba da haɗin taimako na taimako akan shafin Shiga ga URL ɗin. Ba a nuna idan ƙimar ba komai.
tooltip.manager_expiration: Yawan seconds har sai an dauki manajan dindindin, a lokacin da za'a cire rikodin manajan kocin daga bayanan. Darajar 0 yana hana rajistar karewa.
tooltip.max_login_attempts: Yawan ƙoƙarin shiga ba daidai ba kafin a kulle asusun. Wannan saitin kawai ya shafi asusun gida.
tooltip.minimize_local_logging: Lokacin amfani da mafita mai nisa kamar SPUNKK, rage girman bayanan bayanan bayanan bayanan gida don mafi kyawun scalalables.
tooltip.primary_manager_timeout: Yawan seconds har sai an dauki manajan farko. Idan sauran manajoji suna da rai wanda zai karɓi mafi girma na farko.
tooltip.provision_timeout: Matsakaicin lokacin da za a jira don auto-da aka buga don shiga ciki kuma ya zama akwai. Bayan wannan lokacin ya wuce, ana lalata VM ta atomatik.
tooltip.registration_token: Alen da aka yi amfani da su don yin rajista da sabbin kayan aikin don tura hannu.
tooltip.same_site: Sanya sifa da sifishin Sihiri don matsakaiciyar http ɗin HTTP. Zaɓuɓɓukan inganci sune LX, tsayayye kuma babu.
tooltip.same_zone_reply: Idan aka saita zuwa gaskiya, manajan zai ba da amsa ga wakili na kai tare da jerin manajoji a cikin yankin iri ɗaya ne. In ba haka ba an bayar da jerin dukkanin manajoji. Wannan ya ba wakiltar jami'ai don kasa ga manajoji a wasu bangarorin.
tooltip.session_lifetime: Yawan sakan zama alama zaman tana aiki.
tooltip.token: Alamar ingantacciyar alama da aka yi amfani da shi a cikin sadarwa tsakanin jami'an Kasm da Manajan API.
tooltip.token_drift_max: Da yawa minti ya kamata a yarda a yarda ya yi rauni.
tooltip.update_check: Wannan saitin zai dakatar da manajan daga bincika tsarin tsarin Kasm.
tooltip.url_endpoint: Endarshen Swenk, mafi kusantar / sabis / mai tara / taron. Don nazarin lokaci zai zama index / _doc /.
tooltip.web_filter_update_url: URL ya yi amfani da shi don sabunta bayanan bayanan yanar gizo
tooltip.cleanup_orphaned_autoscale_servers: Idan tsarin ya katse ko kurakurai a lokacin AutoScaling ana iya samar da sabar a wani bangare kuma tsarin na iya rasa hanyar uwar garken da ke maraya.
